{"tid":986583,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"爆N年前淒涼史 謝安琪珠海酒吧三陪","createTime":"2019-01-18T14:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T08:53:49.000Z","uid":197644,"like":5,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"59cc83033b79d6bf49f2961bd36fd833765189cb","tid":986583,"uid":197644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.scmedia.com.hk/scm_photos/THREEWEEKLY/200904/81814/444821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmedia.com.hk%2Fscm_photos%2FTHREEWEEKLY%2F200904%2F81814%2F444821.jpg&h=06c7bebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在數年前仍是寂寂無名，為生計更遠赴珠海酒吧做騷，其間要「陪唱」、「陪玩」、「陪飲」，而面對如狼似虎，醉酒失控的酒客，謝安琪只能委屈陪住笑，與今天出騷十多人前呼後擁保護的情景，認真差天共地。<br />\n<br />\n對於當日有天后級人馬於珠海酒吧賣唱，當中有駐場制服囡囡大爆料，指謝安琪扮Stephy很可愛，並說︰「佢唱歌嘅死仔。」<br />\n<br />\n日前，本刊向謝安琪問到酒吧賣唱淒涼史，她似乎不想再提當年的辛酸經歷，不斷講「係好耐之前嘅事。」、「歌酬幾多都唔記得晒。」"},{"pid":"d15128c026560c1f61d9b003293bf26a53b6e4b1","tid":986583,"uid":158613,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"要養謝繼聰"},{"pid":"8c8632768d1e3b7785a64609f0a09d5f2d4b8e25","tid":986583,"uid":197644,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"d15128c026560c1f61d9b003293bf26a53b6e4b1","tid":986583,"uid":158613,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"要養謝繼聰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"陰公琪琪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff26e0f39348bc2f31564a789a53bfe586f8df2e","tid":986583,"uid":37220,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"在數年前仍是寂寂無名，為生計更遠赴珠海酒吧做騷<br />\n<br />\nfail la"},{"pid":"258743c4c1f9ddecf4ce988d5e29ed7bfb190c7a","tid":986583,"uid":76115,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"佢咁撚樣衰"},{"pid":"a44d7992ce793fd9462309dc46f720d2195fe819","tid":986583,"uid":4917,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019